title: SPY Sleighs it in SoCal
description: The SPY holiday helpers recently delivered holiday cheer to local retailers Spyder, ZJ's Boarding House and Val Surf. Freaky Santa and his elf embarked in their reindeer van with baskets filled with sunglasses, snow goggles, summer sausages and SPY beverages to show gratitude to our shops and the kids who rock it. Keep your eyes out for the SPY holiday team as they continue sleigh'n it for the holidays.
